io.hekate.core.service

Interface ClusterContext


  • public interface ClusterContext
    Context for ClusterService.

    This interface is attended to providing feedback from a ClusterService back to the Hekate instance. However other services can also use it in order to obtain current cluster topology or register cluster event listeners.

    See Also:
    InitializationContext.cluster()
